6/ Remember all it takes is one good trade to make it big & grow your portfolio

You can have 10 bad plays chasing the pump of the day then make it all back by making one good play ie. coolmans universe 0.3eth‚Äì>2.6eth

Whats the lesson ?

5/ Everyone has an entry strategy but never an exit strategy, why?

Emotions drive us and lead us both consciously and unconsciously

If you feel the need to check floor prices everyday/every hour/ every min

You have too much invested

4/ The goal of an investor in the space is to preserve your capital 

Think longterm

Do not set yourself up for failure by over leveraging in trades based off emotion 

Not everything that glitters is gold, dont fall in love with all your plays

3/ Most of my best plays came from the alpha groups i have access to through owning nfts and being a dynamic participant in the space

1/ We all get access to the same information most of the time
